column3: alternating in small batches of 4 lemmas x28. train on frequent then infrequent batches
column4: do swapping between questions and statemnts for the first 14 batches
column5: then only questions for the next 14 batches. give only context as example sentence. for training: 32 high frequency
column7: all sumerian/emesal. test batch size = 50. small mistake correction (thresh 3)
column9: and negative reinforcement used in training. Example sentence masks turned on.
